{"id": 5896, "title": "Ticket #5896: Move tmpfiles configuration to /usr/lib/tmpfiles.d/", "description": "<blockquote>\nSystemd config owned by the package should live in <code>/usr</code>. Relevant JIRA ticket: <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://jira.opensciencegrid.org/browse/SOFTWARE-2447\">https://jira.opensciencegrid.org/browse/SOFTWARE-2447</a>.\n\n<p>Additionally, I removed the call to <code>systemd-tmpfiles</code> to create the folders in <code>/var/run/</code> and <code>/var/lock</code>, electing to instead create them via standard RPM <code>%files</code> method. This appears to be recommended: <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Packaging:Tmpfiles.d\">https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Packaging:Tmpfiles.d</a>.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2016-Sep-15 11:40:45 by tim:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>CODE REVIEW:</strong> Thank you for the update, Brian. It looks good.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"attach_get/966/tmpfiles.patch\">tmpfiles.patch</a>\n1574 bytes added by blin on 2016-Sep-12 21:54:17 UTC.\n</li><li><a href=\"attach_get/967/0001-Move-tmpfiles-configuration-to-usr-lib-tmpfiles.d.patch\">0001-Move-tmpfiles-configuration-to-usr-lib-tmpfiles.d.patch</a>\n1951 bytes added by blin on 2016-Sep-15 15:47:27 UTC.\n<br/>\nFixing patch format<br/>\n</li></ul>\n</blockquote>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Sep-23 15:10</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=49283\">[49283]</a></span>: Version history for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5896\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5896'); return false;\" title=\"Move tmpfiles configuration to /usr/lib/tmpfiles.d/\">#5896</a>